自己的球拍。」 王楚钦球拍被踩后续：摄影经理已记下记者证件号，正在调查此事"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-9d349f525a2eb78bdbacb2be4a14220c_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "68 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/663163109"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI4uaP6tnUy5lpEAMaCTEwOTY0NzMxMCDFxqy1BjAAOLMBQApyCTY2MzE2MzEwOXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1722514341.886057", "card_id": "Q_396740369", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 28}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "哪些时候你觉得孩子的成长需要一点「体育精神」？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-f708f0dc959891e3f9c9927b27c18957_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "65 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/396740369"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I4uaP6tnUy5lpEAMaCDUwNDQzOTgwIJH0ovYFMAA4LUALcgkzOTY3NDAzNjl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1722514341.886254", "card_id": "Q_661818788", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 23}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "大家都说夏天穿衣越简单越好看，那你是怎么打扮简单不廉价?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-873f94610c068cd99c76b67f0782d2c1_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": ""